

Running tests
-------------

Use::

  host:~/SoundCloudAPI deets$ nosetests -sw scapi/tests/ test_connect:test_setting_permissions

to run a specific test, or::

  host:~/SoundCloudAPI deets$ nosetests -sw scapi/tests/ test_connect

to run the whole suite.


Creating the API-docs
---------------------

Do::
   epydoc -v --name="SoundCloud API" --html -o docs/api scapi --exclude="os|mimetypes|urllib2|exceptions|mimetools"

